---
// Mission section — dark background with centered message
---

<section id="mission" class="bg-brand-dark py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-6">
      Every Purchase Helps a Pet in Need
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-white/80 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      We partner with local shelters and rescue organizations. A portion of every sale
      goes directly to feeding, sheltering, and finding forever homes for pets in need.
      When you shop with Pet & Paint, you are making a real difference.
    </p>
    <a
      href="#"
      class="inline-block bg-white text-brand-dark px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-brand-cream transition-colors"
    >
      Learn More
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
